<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><div><font face="arial">We received the online portion of your application for the winter 2020 edition of NY NOW®&nbsp;and are happy to hear of your interest in Accent on Design®.</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">Accent on Design is a juried section of the market and as such applications are reviewed by an independent selection committee. To be considered the committee requires that you <u><b>mail</b></u> a comprehensive packet with supporting material. Your application packet must arrive in our office by <b><u>October 15th</u></b>&nbsp;and should include the following:&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br>•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Designer/company statement - <u>include specific details about the innovation behind the products</u>&nbsp;(i.e. materials, process, function)</font></div><div><br></div><div><font face="arial">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Catalog/brochure indicating the products you plan to exhibit</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Wholesale pricing</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Booth display photo (reflecting your display plans)</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>10-20 examples of your current customer base</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">It is important to keep your application materials clear and concise – giving the committee all of the information they need but in a streamlined fashion. If you have any questions please let us know.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial"><b>NOTE:</b> Materials received after October 15th may not be able to be reviewed by the selection committee for consideration in the&nbsp;winter 2020 market.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">For submission details and ”tips on applying to a juried section” please visit: <a href="http://www.nynow.com/exhibitors/tips-on-applying">http://www.nynow.com/exhibitors/tips-on-applying</a>​ &nbsp;&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">Please mail your application to:&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">Emerald Expositions</font></div><div><font face="arial">ATTN: Accent on Design Applications&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial">1133 Westchester Avenue, Suite N210&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial">White Plains, NY 10604-3547&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">If you have any further questions, please feel free to contact us. Otherwise, we look forward to receiving your application.&nbsp;</font></div><div><br></div><div><font face="arial">Sincerely,</font></div><div><br></div><div><div><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Andrea Colagiovanni | Sales Manager | 914-421-3280</span></div></div></div>]]></td>
